
# Product Category & Upgradation

## 1. Available Product Categories
| Category | Amount | Notes |
|----------|--------|------|
| Category 1 | 500    | Free registration |
| Category 2 | 1000   |  |
| Category 3 | 2000   |  |
| Category 4 | 5000   |  |
| Category 5 | 10000  |  |

## 2. Upgradation Rules
- Users can upgrade from **any lower category to any higher category**.
- **Each category can be upgraded only one time.**
- Purchasing the **same category again** is treated as **repurchase**.
- Purchasing **any lower category after a higher category is already active** is treated as **repurchase**.
- There are **no conditional restrictions** on upgradation.
- Moving from a higher category to a lower category is **not allowed as upgradation**.
## 3. Notes
- Any special rules, exceptions, or future updates will be added here. here.
